# Application secrets, credentials, and sensitive configuration files
**/config/credentials.*
**/config/secrets.*
**/keys/
**/passwords/
**/private/
**/secrets/
*.auth
*.authz
*.password
*.secret
*.secrets
*.token
*_tokens
